      "updated": 1774904476259,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Running each 5m:\n— delayed in query | 5m delayed on execution\n— future looking | task should be run within 5m | sleep(4.9m) -> down ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Running each 5m:\n— delayed in query | 5m delayed on execution\n— future looking | task should be run within 5m | sleep(4.9m) -> down ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "esZcWKtQ2RyIYp8YPcS08",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2221.5561707351985,
      "y": -66.00358329034316,
      "width": 668.799072265625,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "HfPvguYP2Zj0SUORX2wdk"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2B",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 102725349,
      "version": 634,
      "versionNonce": 278466789,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774904476259,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Every 2s:\n100 every second ~ 200 every two second\nfor Dozens of Task it would be relatively large 10k-20k and \n    would burn 2s threshold even with proper indexing some ±500ms\nAdditionally: \n   running this expensive query every 2s will overwhelm DB\n   and my affect of GET endpoints and users can not see status of their jobs",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Every 2s:\n100 every second ~ 200 every two second\nfor Dozens of Task it would be relatively large 10k-20k and \n    would burn 2s threshold even with proper indexing some ±500ms\nAdditionally: \n   running this expensive query every 2s will overwhelm DB\n   and my affect of GET endpoints and users can not see status of their jobs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
